events.name: SS Give Boo Repellent
events.asm:
; NAME: SS Give Boo Repellent
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct

ADDIU SP SP -48 ; Including 4 byte pad
SW RA 40(SP)
SW S2 36(SP)
SW S1 32(SP)
SW S0 28(SP)

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex
NOP

; Figure out which player item slots to fill
ADDU S0 R0 R0

LUI S1 hi(p1_item1)
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(p1_item1)

BEQ S0 V0 determineslot
NOP
ADDIU S0 S0 1

LUI S1 hi(p2_item1)
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(p2_item1)

BEQ S0 V0 determineslot
NOP
ADDIU S0 S0 1

LUI S1 hi(p3_item1)
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(p3_item1)

BEQ S0 V0 determineslot
NOP
ADDIU S0 S0 1

LUI S1 hi(p4_item1)
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(p4_item1)

; Figure out if the current player can even fit the item
determineslot:
ADDIU S2 R0 0xFF
LBU S0 0(S1)
BEQ S0 S2 giverepellent ; First slot empty (0xFF)
NOP
ADDIU S1 S1 1
LBU S0 0(S1)
BEQ S0 S2 giverepellent
NOP
ADDIU S1 S1 1
LBU S0 0(S1)
BEQ S0 S2 giverepellent
NOP

; If we reached here, the player has too many items.
SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
ADDI A0 R0 -1 ; Character image (-1 for none)
LUI A1 hi(cannotGiveItemMsg)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(cannotGiveItemMsg)
ADDU A2 R0 R0
JAL 0x800EC8EC ; ShowMessage
ADDU A3 R0 R0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP
J exit
NOP

giverepellent:
SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
ADDI A0 R0 -1 ; Character image (-1 for none)
LUI A1 hi(gotRepellentMsg)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(gotRepellentMsg)
ADDU A2 R0 R0
JAL 0x800EC8EC ; ShowMessage
ADDU A3 R0 R0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

ADDIU S2 R0 0x0C ; Boo Repellent value
SB S2 0(S1)

JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 R0 0x10E ; hidden block sound effect

exit:
LW RA 40(SP)
LW S2 36(SP)
LW S1 32(SP)
LW S0 28(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 48


.align 16
cannotGiveItemMsg:
.byte 0x05 ; green
.ascii "Mamar "
.byte 0x08 ; white
.ascii "Come back and get this "
.byte 0x06 ; yellow
.byte 0x0A ; \n
.ascii "Boo Repellent "
.byte 0x08 ; white
.ascii "when you have room"
.byte 0x85 ; .
.byte 0xFF,0 ; FF=Pause

.align 16
gotRepellentMsg:
.byte 0x05 ; green
.ascii "Mamar "
.byte 0x08 ; white
.ascii "Protect yourself with a "
.byte 0x06 ; yellow
.byte 0x0A ; \n
.ascii "Boo Repellent"
.byte 0x08 ; white
.byte 0x85 ; .
.ascii " Begone"
.byte 0x82 ; ,
.ascii " fiend"
.byte 0xC2 ; !
.byte 0xC2, 0x16, 0x19
.byte 0xFF,0 ; FF=Pause

events.id: SS GIVE RANDOM COINS IN RANGE
events.name: SS Give Random Coins in Range
events.asm:
; NAME: SS Give Random Coins in Range
; GAMES: MP1_USA,MP2_USA,MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct

ADDIU SP SP -8
SW RA 4(SP)
SW S0 0(SP)

.definelabel MAX_COINS,12

JAL guRandom ; Generates random 32-bit int
NOP
; Random int was returned in V0

divide:
ADDIU T0 R0 MAX_COINS
DIVU V0 T0 ; V0 / T0
MFHI S0 ; HI contains the remainder, pull that into S0

; Get the current player index
JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex
NOP

; Give the player the coins
ADDIU A0 V0 0
ADDU A1 S0 R0
JAL AdjustPlayerCoins
NOP

; Display the coin change by the player stats
JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex
NOP
ADDIU A0 V0 0
JAL ShowPlayerCoinChange
ADDU A1 S0 R0

; Sleep for 30 frames to let coin change take effect
JAL SleepProcess
ADDIU A0 R0 30

LW RA 4(SP)
LW S0 0(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 8

LBU S0 0(S1)
BEQ S0 S2 givelamp
NOP

; If we reached here, the player has too many items.
SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
ADDI A0 R0 -1 ; Character image (-1 for none)
LUI A1 hi(cannotGiveItemMsg)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(cannotGiveItemMsg)
ADDU A2 R0 R0
JAL 0x800EC8EC ; ShowMessage
ADDU A3 R0 R0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP
J exit
NOP

givelamp:
SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
ADDI A0 R0 -1 ; Character image (-1 for none)
LUI A1 hi(gotLampMsg)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(gotLampMsg)
ADDU A2 R0 R0
JAL 0x800EC8EC ; ShowMessage
ADDU A3 R0 R0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

ADDIU S2 R0 0x0E ; Magic Lamp value
SB S2 0(S1)

JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 R0 0x10E ; hidden block sound effect

exit:
LW RA 40(SP)
LW S2 36(SP)
LW S1 32(SP)
LW S0 28(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 48


.align 16
cannotGiveItemMsg:
.byte 0x05 ; green
.ascii "Eldstar "
.byte 0x08 ; white
.ascii "Come back and get this "
.byte 0x06 ; yellow
.byte 0x0A ; \n
.ascii "Magic Lamp "
.byte 0x08 ; white
.ascii "when you have room"
.byte 0x85 ; .
.byte 0xFF,0 ; FF=Pause

.align 16
gotLampMsg:
.byte 0x05 ; green
.ascii "Eldstar "
.byte 0x08 ; white
.ascii "Take this "
.byte 0x07 ; yellow
.ascii "Magic Lamp"
.byte 0x08 ; white
.byte 0x0A ; \n
.ascii "and soar to the star"
.byte 0xC2 ; !
.byte 0xC2, 0x16, 0x19
.byte 0xFF,0 ; FF=Pause
